Nicholas J. MILETICH v. C. H. LOONEY, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Leavenworth, Kansas. No. 5767. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. March 12, 1958. Jerry N. Snyder, Denver, Colo., for appellant. William C. Farmer, U. S. Atty., and E. Edward Johnson, Asst. U. S. Atty., Topeka, Kan., for appellee.

Before PICKETT, LEWIS and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed without written opinion.
